OL,6,FLurgan man Colin Duffy, 56, whose
OL,7,Faddress was given as HMP Maghaberry
OL,8,Fand Fitzsimons, also 56 and from
OL,9,FDunmore Mews in Belfast, were charged
OL,10,Fwith offences arising from a gun
OL,11,Fattack on a police convoy in the
OL,12,FArdoyne area of north Belfast on
OL,13,FDecember 5, 2013.
