OL,3,CColin Duffy and Henry Fitzsimons
OL,4,Cacquitted of terrorism charges
OL,6,FThe charges included preparing and
OL,7,Fdirecting terrorism, and membership or
OL,8,Fprofessing to be members of the IRA,
OL,9,Fwhilst Mr Fitzsimons was also charged
OL,10,Fwith attempting to murder police in
OL,11,Fthe convoy on December 6, 2013, and
OL,12,Fpossessing the two AK47 assault rifles
OL,13,Fand ammunition.
OL,15,FThe day after the shooting, a total of
OL,16,F14 covert devices secretly recorded a
OL,17,Fconversation between three men in the
OL,18,FLurgan Park areas of the Co Armagh
OL,19,Ftown.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/7
