OL,4,Cacquitted of terrorism charges
OL,6,FThe discussion concerned the gun
OL,7,Fattack which took place the night
OL,8,Fbefore as well as future operation -
OL,9,Fand it was the Crown's case that Mr
OL,10,FFitzsimons and Mr Duffy were two of
OL,11,Fthe three men recorded.
OL,13,FThe prosecution contended that the
OL,14,Fnames 'Collie' and 'Harry' could be
OL,15,Fheard on the audio.
OL,17,FOther parts of the Crown's evidence
OL,18,Fwas the presence of a silver Lexus,
OL,19,Fwhich was the same make and model as
OL,20,FMr Fitzsimon's car and which was in
OL,21,FLurgan at the appropriate times.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/7
