OL,6,FDuring the trial, several experts were
OL,7,Fcalled to give evidence about the
OL,8,Faudio recordings, which were also
OL,9,Fcarefully considered by Mr Justice
OL,10,FO'Hara.
OL,12,FAs he gave his ruling today, the Judge
OL,13,Fsaid it would be "unsafe" to reply on
OL,14,Fhis own impression of the audio
OL,15,Fevidence given the "clear warnings"
OL,16,Ffrom the experts for both the Crown
OL,17,Fand defence.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/7
