OL,3,CColin Duffy and Henry Fitzsimons
OL,4,Cacquitted of terrorism charges
OL,6,FMr Justice O'Hara said: "In light of
OL,7,Fthis conclusion I cannot say that I am
OL,8,Fsatisfied to the requisite standard
OL,9,Fthat the audio evidence proves that
OL,10,Feither Fitzsimons or Duffy was in the
OL,11,Flane in Lurgan Park on the afternoon
OL,12,Fof the 6th of December, 2013.
OL,14,F"The reasonable and legitimate
OL,15,Fsuspicions raised about their presence
OL,16,Fand their intent from other evidence
OL,17,Fare not enough to form the basis of a
OL,18,Fconviction of either of them.
OL,20,F"In these circumstances, I find both
OL,21,Fdefendants not guilty on all charges."
